# Minimal profile: Base interpreters + display-function overrides + command paths
#
# This profile installs only the essential variables needed for basic operation:
# - Core interpreters (TERMINAL, COMBINATOR, BATCH_COMBINATOR)
# - Command paths and binaries (PATH, PFCTL, WG_QUICK, OPENVPN, etc.)
# - Display-only function overrides (list, validate, info, help, status, etc.)
#
# Security model:
# - TERMINAL_INTERPRETER defaults to 'cat' (display-only, safe by default)
# - COMBINATOR_INTERPRETER uses 'xargs env' (recursive execution)
# - BATCH_COMBINATOR_INTERPRETER processes multiple commands
#
# Display-only function overrides are pinned to 'cat' to ensure they remain
# display-only even when users opt-in to execution by setting
# TERMINAL_INTERPRETER=sh in .env/local/
#
# Users customize behavior by adding overrides to .env/local/
# See DEPLOYMENT.md for configuration workflow.
